# Model config: Qwen3-Coder-Next (UD-Q5_K_M)
#
# 80B MoE with only ~3B active params (~46 GiB at this quant). Fits Strix Halo's unified
# memory but NOT the R9700's 32 GiB, so run it on strixhalo (Vulkan).
#
# Rationale:
#   - N_CPU_MOE keeps this many MoE expert layers in CPU/system RAM. On unified memory the
#     GPU still reaches them, freeing GTT for the dense layers + a big KV cache. 40 is a
#     good start; lower it (more on GPU) if you have headroom, raise it if OOM.
#   - Built for agentic coding at long context; the strixhalo profile's large ctx + q8_0 KV
#     keep that cache affordable.
#   - Qwen3-Coder sampling: temp 0.7, top-p 0.8, top-k 20, repeat-penalty 1.05.

: "${MODEL:=Qwen3-Coder-Next/Qwen3-Coder-Next-UD-Q5_K_M.gguf}"
: "${N_CPU_MOE:=40}"

LLAMA_ARGS+=(--n-cpu-moe "${N_CPU_MOE}" --temp 0.7 --top-p 0.8 --top-k 20 --repeat-penalty 1.05)
